# Spec Completion Checklist

- Confirm SPEC_PRODUCT_READY: true is already set in spec.md before starting.
- Review ADR Technical Decision Layer — confirm, adjust, or override with documented rationale.
- Validate Mermaid diagrams (correct type, accurate component names).
- Remove the agent draft block-quote notice from the ADR.
- Set ADR technical decision sign-off: approved in the ADR metadata.
- Set ADR Status: approved.
- Record Architecture sign-off: approved in spec.md.
- Record Security sign-off: approved in spec.md.
- Record Operations sign-off: approved in spec.md.
- Set SPEC_READY: true in spec.md.
- Run make quality-sdd-check — must pass with SPEC_READY: true.
- Commit spec.md and ADR file to the existing Draft PR branch.
- Confirm no new PR was opened.
